{"tid":644742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「新」iPhone7賣$4,000　內地漢中伏","createTime":"2018-04-27T12:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T13:07:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dd26e14f1c8a7ad58b44eabfa44961d343556d09","tid":644742,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180427/20374475?_ga=2.12308276.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180427%2F20374475%3F_ga%3D2.12308276.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=uqcMyvfCwrYngX29a6Qhgo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fd7bfbfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180427%2F20374475%3F_ga%3D2.12308276.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=cf182470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180427/20374475?_ga=2.12308276.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n「新」iPhone7賣$4,000　內地漢中伏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180427/large/a2106a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180427%2Flarge%2Fa2106a.gif&h=0051d389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■金先生指圖中先達店員承認以舊機當新機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旺角先達廣場近日好紅：一星期前被海關掃場，日前港鐵手機冒煙事故女事主又話部機喺先達買，連子華黃牛飛都登陸先達，啱啱仲有單手機投訴關先達事。有位喺香港金融機構工作、初為人父嘅內地人金先生爆料，月中打算買部大容量嘅256GB iPhone7，但官網得128GB賣，原本對先達冇咩信心嘅佢喺朋友提議下去碰吓運氣。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n金先生話佢本月13日喺先達一間店舖賣256GB嘅iPhone7，索價4,000元，較原裝機7,188元平近一半，佢當時都好疑惑，不過個店員話出咗iPhone8及iPhone X，iPhone7過晒氣同係倉底貨，因此劈價促銷。店員講到似層層，佢就買咗一部，開機又正常操作，駁電腦check機至發現係翻新機，立刻向店方質詢，對方亦願意退款。最終金生成功退款，但坦言「太失望，以為內地遍地假貨，沒想香港也這樣」。更直斥店舖缺德，以後不會到先達買手機。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180427/large/a2106b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180427%2Flarge%2Fa2106b.gif&h=8eded46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 中式深蹲熱爆　考起外國人<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點●即聽"},{"pid":"fbf21b0ed820f73d155eab37a1f1deaadfe2a287","tid":644742,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"金融才俊都比人呃到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c1fbe1e6e29aa8eef150fec89f40598b8a83fa","tid":644742,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"先達行貨"},{"pid":"669423744f8195254592a194b7858990f61d2db8","tid":644742,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/211038_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F211038_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=2509d6b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c409febdc3cdef9a5a0d48c93a9c02e71b867ed","tid":644742,"uid":174079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"去先達買行貨我真係恭喜你呀"},{"pid":"24a6f78f4fe7a6fb455421985afdade640a43bf6","tid":644742,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"水行貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db13259364c1dbcd89c7a6bb97dfad7143140a31","tid":644742,"uid":34010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:38:14.000Z","msg":"成功退款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6992d7c9aa16657469b44b83ad2f2d78d4b201f","tid":644742,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n救撚命啊重有人喺先達買手機"},{"pid":"f85bcb56a117c45774d0bc111639fd343d26d3d3","tid":644742,"uid":44486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:39:57.000Z","msg":"退款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2932d3b0677cd46d169e66df58fa6af31848efe3","tid":644742,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T13:07:20.000Z","msg":"竟然退到款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}